{"tid":274924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港隊長陳偉豪告別港隊: 「你們1分鐘的掌聲，是我用17年堆砌得來的。」","createTime":"2017-06-07T16:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T06:10:00.000Z","uid":9030,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64a1af079175593360d8c954a2679198573ae962","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/000521_bacd673aadc72c256932ac3c611a1efc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F000521_bacd673aadc72c256932ac3c611a1efc.jpg&h=492c218b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偉豪臨別感言亦流露搞笑本色：「做球員永遠都唔知道下一場比賽係幾時，今場比賽係我最享受同最珍惜，因為知道唔係自己踢先。喺度特別多謝一班隊友踢出一場精彩比賽，唔知係咪因為我嘅關係好搏，好似李志豪、林嘉緯、盧均宜；仲有後期嘅葉鴻輝，我哋一齊經歷過唔少大小戰役，冇咗你哋，我嘅港隊回憶一定冇咁完美。今日有呢個儀式，唔代表我嘅地位比大家高，只係我年紀大啲，要行先一步。」 <br />\n<br />\n說到此刻，偉豪難掩感性，呼籲球迷繼續支持香港足球員：「喺呢個時候離開係最適合，見到唔少有質素嘅年輕球員，大家都係用青春為港隊效力，每一位都係願意為香港隊犧牲嘅英雄。特別感謝球迷為我搵番唔少香港隊紀錄，仲有第15分鐘嘅掌聲，雖然只係1分鐘，但係我用17年堆砌得嚟。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/000535_28dfbb939f03bb5fc0c0f5bd4a2049d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F000535_28dfbb939f03bb5fc0c0f5bd4a2049d2.jpg&h=b8020a12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c172a79695c79cff7c323fdaa2bf2e4f3250cf2","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/000706_29475e6c74784a2070ed8df4930af26c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F000706_29475e6c74784a2070ed8df4930af26c.jpg&h=6f61e395&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07560496a9211dcbdc9f09ca05b0484acdda8751","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/000900_da5be150eac57d764dfaa048a5db62d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F000900_da5be150eac57d764dfaa048a5db62d2.jpg&h=38dccd46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/000901_d1f0f0915ea51f0939e2d4db20750030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F000901_d1f0f0915ea51f0939e2d4db20750030.jpg&h=d7fcfd9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29b6726c9557f7789a5a15f3611a913139af48ab","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"國際熱身賽香港主場出擊，最終同約旦打成0:0平手，呢場亦係陳偉豪嘅告別戰，賽後佢發出告別感言，更一度哽咽，場面感人。偉豪離開球場之時，有為數過百球迷圍住偶像，要偉豪影相簽名留念，Fans們送禮物又送蛋糕，偉豪當然開心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170608/photo/bkn-20170608003744241-0608_00882_001_02b.jpg?20170608004450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170608%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170608003744241-0608_00882_001_02b.jpg%3F20170608004450&h=24992bdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7ede4733fa964be3e10b81aba300933ad3621b4","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170607/large/1496847946_19d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170607%2Flarge%2F1496847946_19d9.jpg&h=098bc8a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85060e163226da0968cd2e50bf663847a71bd4b8","tid":274924,"uid":90038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:00:19.000Z","msg":"三千人都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f925ac52bb5d867f906789bccafc30034a3ac51d","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/QM1rTG2pT3Jra/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FQM1rTG2pT3Jra%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7dbed8f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50256d7e4d96b6b9b0e8f6c8a0bea4f76552de2c","tid":274924,"uid":84392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c176944cf8195aee231cdc8c963b89c7d3e96a1b","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喊左出黎 唉 咁就一個年代 特別係佢仲捱過冰河</blockquote><br />\n事實佢係跨年代icon"},{"pid":"f7f101357a17525e9a79def6d5872c5ec46cd67d","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"正式告別港足，豪哥亦感謝隊友、球迷、足總、金判坤等為他帶來難忘的回憶：「多謝球迷在15分鐘為我拍掌，我感受到這一分鐘真真正正屬於我，隊友在我旁邊也有拍，多謝大家的心意。我們差點入球時我激動得彈了起身，感謝隊友給予我這樣美好的回憶。」"},{"pid":"894cfe929ebcf2583ebc0788f06d095f5e3fc17d","tid":274924,"uid":84392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13420b6286b6aec5c39e5b5d4320060953e08ee6","tid":274924,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:34:44.000Z","msg":"同葉鴻輝個樣一樣"},{"pid":"b1aab134cde4e619faf53d85d2c42811dab73ed8","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"大港腳生涯以1：1作客和阿聯酋展開、以0：0主場和約旦終結，與西亞勁旅交手縱未取勝也讓陳偉豪心滿意足。亞洲盃外圍賽兩和烏茲別克、東亞盃外圍賽擊敗朝鮮，65場國際A級賽，將近5300分鐘上陣時間，完場笛聲響起代表著「豪歌」的國際賽生涯結束，17年大港腳生涯一幕幕在腦海中閃過。「可能這些畫面在我腦海中只有1分鐘，但這1分鐘讓我看出了17年時間的堆砌。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/06/20170607_%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B32_UP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F06%2F20170607_%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B32_UP.jpg&h=0b5031f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就如陳偉豪在賽後記者會上所言，相隔近2年再戰國際賽，仍然感到面對強隊絲毫不能放鬆，這名港足「老大哥」在72分鐘於觀眾的掌聲中登場，到比賽最後階段更表現出其「路數」，看穿約旦的罰球戰術，及時阻止對方球員在禁區頂的射門，也讓港足保住「清白身」，「豪歌」得以一場和局完成在大港腳最後一戰。」<br />\n<br />\n「每場比賽都好深刻。」陳偉豪在賽後表示，在場每名港足球員都「用他們的青春為港足効力，每一位都是英雄，每一位都值得大家驕傲」，他感謝老戰友林嘉緯、李志豪、盧均宜、葉鴻輝伴其同行多年：「給我好多難忘回憶，沒他們陪伴我，一定失色不少。」<br />\n<br />\n陳偉豪在完場後將今晚的比賽用球贈予球迷，並且向看台上的觀眾道別，隊友們列隊與其擊掌致敬與及將他拋起，「豪歌」之後表示：「作為香港隊球員，你永遠不會知道自己最後一場比賽是何時，所以我好珍惜每場比賽，17年來我的得著比付出多，好多難忘回憶都來自港隊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/06/20170607_%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B3%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA15_UP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F06%2F20170607_%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA15_UP.jpg&h=3eef9cbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce910d59db8db5316983b2bc9a2c54cb156e218","tid":274924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:04:28.000Z","msg":"高梵也準備了特別髮型歡送陳偉豪 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/06/20170607_%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B3%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA3_UP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F06%2F20170607_%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA3_UP.jpg&h=317078bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dad72ff7592dbea0cbc2c682f574db465ce7bcc4","tid":274924,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高梵也準備了特別髮型歡送陳偉豪 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/06/20170607_%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B3%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA3_UP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F06%2F20170607_%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA3_UP.jpg&h=317078bf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e6c78f350174a74cdcb190fc6f40c04fbe92e1","tid":274924,"uid":269,"like":0,"di